message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product. I think you'll really love it! I'm willing to sell it to you for $110.
Thanks for the offer, Alice! I'm really interested in the product, but $110 is a bit high for me. Could you do $90?
I understand you're looking for a better deal, Bob. I'm willing to meet you halfway, but I need to make a profit. I can offer it to you for $100.
